@startuml
' Diagram: F07 - Ghi nhan phi duy tri va lich su hoa don POI (Sequence)
' Status: VERIFIED
' Baseline: branch master, current worktree @ HEAD 2497a96
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/ThanhToan/Index.cshtml.cs: OnGetAsync()
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/ThanhToan/GhiNhan.cshtml.cs: OnGetAsync(), OnPostAsync(), LoadPoiAsync()
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/ThanhToan/LichSu.cshtml.cs: OnGetAsync()
' Note: Sequence mo ta chi tiet luong Razor PageModel hien tai, gom moc gia han, upsert DangKyDichVu, va tao HoaDon theo tung thang; khong suy dien them PaymentController du phong.
title F07 - Ghi nhan phi duy tri va lich su hoa don POI

actor Admin
participant "ThanhToan/IndexModel" as IndexModel
participant "GhiNhanModel" as GhiNhanModel
participant "LichSuModel" as LichSuModel
participant AppDbContext
database DB

Admin -> IndexModel: mo /ThanhToan
IndexModel -> AppDbContext: load POIs + DangKyDichVus active + HoaDons(thang hien tai)
AppDbContext -> DB: SELECT du lieu thanh toan POI
DB --> AppDbContext: data
IndexModel -> IndexModel: lay PhiDuyTriThang moi nhat theo POI
IndexModel --> Admin: danh sach + thong ke

Admin -> GhiNhanModel: mo /ThanhToan/GhiNhan?poiId=...
GhiNhanModel -> AppDbContext: LoadPoiAsync(poiId)
AppDbContext -> DB: SELECT POI + DangKyDichVu + 5 HoaDon gan nhat
DB --> AppDbContext: data
GhiNhanModel --> Admin: form ghi nhan

Admin -> GhiNhanModel: submit soThangGiaHan, phi, ghiChu
GhiNhanModel -> AppDbContext: load poi + goi hien tai
AppDbContext -> DB: SELECT / INSERT / UPDATE
GhiNhanModel -> GhiNhanModel: neu POI con han -> mocGiaHan = han hien tai\nneu het han -> mocGiaHan = now\ncap nhat POI + upsert DangKyDichVu\ntao HoaDon theo tung ky yyyy-MM
AppDbContext -> DB: SaveChanges()
DB --> AppDbContext: saved
GhiNhanModel --> Admin: redirect /ThanhToan?msg=...

opt xem lich su day du
  Admin -> LichSuModel: mo /ThanhToan/LichSu?poiId=...
  LichSuModel -> AppDbContext: query HoaDons cua POI
  AppDbContext -> DB: SELECT hoadon ORDER BY NgayThanhToan DESC
  DB --> AppDbContext: hoa don
  LichSuModel --> Admin: bang lich su
end
@enduml
